						"documentation" : "After the sender creates a swap, he can optionally call this function to restrict the swap\r\nto a particular receiver address. The swap can't then be claimed by any other receiver.\r\n\n     * Emits a `BuyerSet` event with the created swap hash and new swap hash, updated with\r\nreceiver's address.\r",
						"implemented" : true,
						"isConstructor" : false,
						"kind" : "function",
						"name" : "setBuyer",
						"scope" : 1057,
